library("viridis")

ggplot(data=storms)+
  geom_jitter(aes(x= as.factor(month), y = pressure, fill = wind), pch = 21, alpha = 0.05)+
  scale_fill_viridis_c()+
  theme_bw()+
  labs(title= "Hurricane Pressure v Month", subtitle = "with Max Wind Speed", x = "Month")
